Step:2
disabe cache 3 caches  - block_html, layout, full_page
cmd:    bin/magento cache:disable block_html layout full_page
Result
Changed cache status:
                        layout: 1 -> 0
                    block_html: 1 -> 0
                     full_page: 1 -> 0

Step:3 
Disable cache from browser
window user: ctrl + shift + i
mac user   : cmd  + shift + c
go in network tab and select the checkbox disabel cache.

